INSERT INTO `nitc_channel_content_desc` VALUES (1, 2, '为什么NITC中心会研发NITC效益型网站系统？', 'NITC效益型网站系统就是专门针对中小企业而研发的，是以现代网络营销理念为核心，以搜索引擎良好表现、良好的用户体验为标准，以企业办公应用为增值辅助，能够为企业带来更大效益的企业网站，内置SEO搜索引擎优化机制，多国语言系统。', '为什么NITC中心会研发NITC效益型网站系统？', '', 'NITC效益型网站系统就是专门针对中小企业而研发的，是以现代网络营销理念为核心，以搜索引擎良好表现、良好的用户体验为标准，以企业办公应用为增值辅助，能够为企业带来更大效益的企业网站，内置SEO搜索引擎优化机制，多国语言系统。', '<p>\r\n	NITC组建前一直从事网站建设服务，拥有一批资深的网站技术人才，最早从事网站建设的是1999年开始。2007年NITC组建后，投入了专门部门研究网络营销服务。NITC效益型网站系统是经过近两年时间的研发，2010年6月8日推出V3.0正式版，在此之前是以BETA版（测试）出现。NITC效益型网站系统研发的基础是用网络营销技术制作企业网站。</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	为什么NITC中心会花这么多的时间来研发NITC效益型网站系统呢？<br />\r\n	因为我们发现，虽然网站建设服务在国内这么多年了，但目前国内的中小企业网站普及率还是非常的低，还不到7%。普遍的企业网络意识还不深，只是外贸公司建网站的比例较大一些。而做过网站的一些企业从2006年开始慢慢的偿试做网络营销（PPC竞价、SEO、SEM等），但因不了解SEO的属性，对SEO要求太高，太理想化，导致最终花了昂贵的费用却没有达到理想的效果。通过我们多年对客户的了解，和对客户失败总结的经验，客户普遍忽略了最基础的东西。对于企业而言，网络上最基础的东西莫过于企业网站了。企业网站是企业的门户，是潜在客户了解的前提，所以企业网站的重要性不言而喻。</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	我们NITC网络营销服务中心吸收以往网站系统的优点，结合网络营销知识，注重客户的体验度，把系统的研发方向定位简单化、人性化的趋势。而且提供永久免费的产品下载服务，目的在于普及中小企业网络发展，为中小企业网络营销铺路。企业网站对于大型企业而言，注重的是企业的形象和文化。而对于中小企业而言，更关注的是带来效果，能产生一些潜在客户。我们要郑重声明的是，企业要想在网络上发展，特别是中小企业，就必须注重本身企业网站的建设与维护的重要性。</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	NITC效益型网站系统就是专门针对中小企业而研发的，是以现代网络营销理念为核心，以搜索引擎良好表现、良好的用户体验为标准，以企业办公应用为增值辅助，能够为企业带来更大效益的企业网站，内置SEO搜索引擎优化机制，多国语言系统。我们坚定自己的信念，一定要把产品做好，把免费进行到底！</p>\r\n');
INSERT INTO `nitc_channel_content_desc` VALUES (1, 1, 'Why NITC NITC and efficiency research and development center site system?', 'NITC and efficiency Web site system is specifically developed for SMEs, is the core concept of modern network marketing to search engine, good performance, good user experience as the standard, enterprise office applications for value-added assistance to the SMEs more large effective corporate website, built-in SEO search engine optimization mechanism, multi-language system.', '', '', '', '<p>\r\n	NITC has been involved in site set up before construction, the website has a number of senior technical personnel, is the earliest site construction began in 1999. NITC formed in 2007 after research into a specialized Internet marketing services sector. NITC and efficiency Web site system after nearly two years of R &amp; D, June 8, 2010 launch of the official version V3.0, before that is a BETA version of (test) appears. NITC and efficiency based Web system development is making online marketing technology company website.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Why NITC center will spend so much time to research and development NITC and efficiency site system?<br />\r\n	Because we found that, although site-building services in the country so many years, but prevalence of domestic SMEs site or very low, less than 7%. Common sense of enterprise networks is not deep, but the proportion of foreign trade companies built large number of sites. The company did some of the site began in 2006 slowly been tried to do online marketing (PPC bidding, SEO, SEM, etc.), but did not understand the properties of SEO on SEO too demanding, too idealistic, leading eventually to spend the high costs did not achieve the desired results. Through our many years of understanding the customer, and summed up the experience of failure on the customer, the customer generally ignores the most basic things. For businesses, the most basic things on the network than corporate site. Enterprise is the enterprise portal site, is a potential client to understand the premise, so the importance of corporate Web site is self-evident.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	We absorb the NITC Web Marketing Service Web site the previous system, it combines network marketing knowledge, degree of emphasis on customer experience, to simplify the system of R &amp; D direction of orientation, human tendency. And provide permanent free download services, aimed at popularization of SMEs networks, paving the way for SMEs to network marketing. Corporate Website for large enterprises, the focus is corporate image and culture. For SMEs, the greater concern is to bring results, can produce a number of potential customers. We solemnly declare that the company wants the network development, especially SMEs, must pay attention to their own corporate website&#39;s construction and maintenance of importance.</p>');
INSERT INTO `nitc_channel_content_desc` VALUES (2, 2, '为什么NITC系统暂没有开源？', '我们NITC开发出来的NITC效益型网站系统是完全自己技术团队经过几年时间开发出来的，主要定位是针对中小企业用户，结合我们多年的网络营销知识与经验', '为什么NITC系统暂没有开源？', '', '我们NITC开发出来的NITC效益型网站系统是完全自己技术团队经过几年时间开发出来的，主要定位是针对中小企业用户，结合我们多年的网络营销知识与经验', '<p class=interactiveiofn_right_text1>\r\n	很多人可能问为什么NITC系统没有开源？下面我来说一下我们对这个问题的看法：<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	首先，大家可以看到现在开源的CMS系统有很多，而且时不时的又新冒出几家。但大体结构和功能都差不多，原因是一个出来了，大家都在它的基础上进行修改，然后变成自己的拿出来给用户下载或赢利。我们发现大部分CMS系统功能虽很强大，但操作极为不便，特别是对一般用户而言。可能对技术员来说还好熟悉些，一些专业术语和操作习惯完全只有技术员才搞得懂。而我们NITC开发出来的NITC效益型网站系统是完全自己技术团队经过几年时间开发出来的，主要定位是针对中小企业用户，结合我们多年的网络营销知识与经验。所以会趋向于简单、傻瓜化一些，我们的目的是让大部分人都会操作，而且争取让网站能给用户带来一定的效果。<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	当然，这不代表我们NITC系统就比别的CMS强大，NITC系统比起那些成熟的CMS系统确实存在一些差距，目前还需要不断努力，我们也坚持在创新与完善。只要大家多关注NITC，相信我们NITC就会给大家带来惊喜。请大家拭目以待！<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	目前我们的核心程序是经过安全加密的，很多人要求我们开源，但我们没有开源最主要考虑的三个原因：<br />\r\n	1、系统加密会让核心文件更加安全。若服务器被挂马，木马程序不会感染到核心文件，即便前台页面文件被挂马，只需后台重新生成一下即可。这样，处理木马程序也会变得简单、方便。<br />\r\n	2、NITC效益型网站系统跟我们的计划还有一些距离，需要不断完善。<br />\r\n	3、如果现在开源的话，可能很快也会变成很多个NITC，市场混乱，如果服务体系不完善的公司或个人，这会对终端用户造成影响，就会回到象现在定制网站的价格一样。<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	所以，不是我们不开源，而是要等一定的时期之后我们会完全免费开源的，敬请谅解！</p>\r\n');
INSERT INTO `nitc_channel_content_desc` VALUES (2, 1, 'Why not open temporary NITC system?', 'We developed the NITC NITC Web site and efficiency system is completely their own technical team developed after several years, mainly targeting SMEs user positioning, combined with our years of Internet marketing knowledge and experience.', '', '', '', '<p>\r\n	Many people may ask why the NITC system is not open source? Below me, what we view on this issue:</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	First of all, we can see that there are many open source CMS system, and another from time to time a few new emerge. But the general structure and function are similar, because a out, everyone in it based on the modified, and then into its own in the show to give the user to download Huo profit. We found that although most of the CMS system features a very powerful, but the operation is extremely inconvenient, especially for ordinary users. Technicians who may be familiar to some better, some technical terms and operations used to complete only the technician only Gaode understand. We developed the NITC NITC Web site and efficiency system is completely their own technical team developed after several years, mainly targeting SMEs user positioning, combined with our years of Internet marketing knowledge and experience. Will therefore tend to simple, fool of a number, our goal is to most people would operate, and seek to give users some web results.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Of course, this does not mean we NITC system stronger than the other CMS, NITC system than those who mature CMS system does have some gaps, currently requires constant efforts, we also persisted in innovation and improvement. As long as we pay more attention to NITC, I believe we will give you a surprise NITC. Please wait!</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Our core program is now securely encrypted, and a lot of people ask us to open source, open source, but we do not consider the three main reasons:<br />\r\n	1, the system makes the core file encryption more secure. If the server is hung horse, Trojans do not infect the core file, even if the front page file is linked to Malaysia, just look at the background can be rebuilt. This Trojan horse will handle it easy and convenient.<br />\r\n	2, NITC and efficiency with our program website system some distance from the need to continuously improve.<br />\r\n	3, if we open source it, may soon turn into lots of NITC, market confusion, if imperfect service system companies or individuals, this will impact the end user will return to the site as is now the custom price the same.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	So, not that we do not open source, but have to wait a certain period of time then we will be fully free and open source, after updating?</p>\r\n');
INSERT INTO `nitc_channel_content_desc` VALUES (3, 2, '谁说便宜没好货？！', '产品成败的关键是看谁占有的客户资源多，要获得客户资源首先就应该考虑客户的接受程度及方式！', '谁说便宜没好货？！', '', '产品成败的关键是看谁占有的客户资源多，要获得客户资源首先就应该考虑客户的接受程度及方式！', '<p>\r\n	在一般人来看便宜都是没好货的，而我们却认为便宜未必没好货。主要是看生产商对产品的定位，以及看待市场的眼光而论。眼下任何一种产品竞争都是很大的，产品成败的关键是看谁占有的客户资源多，要获得客户资源首先就应该考虑客户的接受程度及方式。所以，我们认为任何产品不论是便宜还是免费，都必须做好它，不能因为便宜或是免费就随便对待，这样就无法吸引用户，自然也无法迅速发展。我们的NITC效益型网站系统，目前虽然谈不上非常完善，但我们一直在尽自己的能力做好产品细节，让我们的NITC系统在免费软件中发光发热</p>\r\n');
